Vector3.Description: A 3 dimensional vector < x, y, z > with an extra w axis to make it compatible with affine matrix transformations. Comes with a set of built in vector math operations such as arithmetic, normalization, dot, and cross products.
Constructs a new 3D vector with given coordinates.

operator-.ReturnValue: A flipped version of this vector.

Cross.Description: Computes the cross product between two vectors.
